Solve puzzles and blast wooden blocks along the way!

⭐ Endless block puzzle levels and so much fun!
⭐ Super popular game loved by 1M+ players!

🌳 How to Play
* Drag wood block pieces onto the wooden grid.
* Filling a row or column to clear wood blocks.
* Clear multiple lines of wood blocks to earn more points.
* Merge wood blocks in a row to earn more points.
* Beat your highest block puzzle IQ games score.

🌳 Game Features
* Easy to play, but challenging to master!
* Beautiful graphics and satisfying sound effects.
* Relaxing wood block game with no time limit.
* Tetris-like game that all Tetris players would love!
* Best brain trainer and IQ booster.
* Playable offline to enjoy this puzzle game anywhere!

Let's enjoy this simple and addictive 3D Wood Block Puzzle Classic game!
